// Define a large value for infinity, considering the maximum possible cost
// Max path length is N-1. Max cost is 10^9. Max tax is 100.
// Max single edge cost: 10^9 * 100 = 10^11.
// Max path cost: 1000 * 10^11 = 10^14. Use long long.
